275
00:17:34,492 --> 00:17:36,931
D'accord ? Respire calmement, voilà, ok ?

276
00:17:37,802 --> 00:17:38,146
Tout va bien.

277
00:17:38,181 --> 00:17:39,403
Vite, venez.

278
00:17:39,924 --> 00:17:41,146
Tu crois que c'était quoi, Larkin ?

279
00:17:41,808 --> 00:17:43,670
Bien, verrouillez la porte, ok ?

280
00:17:44,319 --> 00:17:44,887
D'accord.

281
00:17:47,292 --> 00:17:47,629
Larkin ?

282
00:17:47,664 --> 00:17:50,191
Ok, Rosie. Pourquoi tu
